0of%20gold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b61cc7f-b91a-4977-89b3-df54ca08349c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20selective%20with%20gold%20stocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20investing%20in%20gold%20stocks%20such%20as%20mining%20companies%2C%20Kertsos%20encourages%20caution.%20While%20gold%20stocks%20can%20offer%20price%20appreciation%2C%20the%20price%20can%20fluctuate%20more%20wildly%20than%20regular%20gold%20bullion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20very%20concentrated%20number%20of%20high-quality%20gold%20stocks%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20very%20long%20tail%20of%20far%20lower-quality%20gold%20stocks%20that%20don't%20necessarily%20deserve%20to%20be%20on%20our%20watch%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20Kertsos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20to%20have%20fairly%20long-duration%20investments%2C%20which%20means%20that%20we%20need%20companies%20that%20have%20long%20mine%20lives%2C%20depth%20in%20the%20management%20team%2C%20good%20sustainability%20practices%2C%20and%20also%20good%20balance%20sheets%2C%26quot%3B%20Kertsos%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20we%20cannot%20find%20any%20such%20company%2C%20we%20will%20keep%20our%20clients'%20capital%20in%20gold%20bullion%20until%20such%20opportunity%20presents%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20assess%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20gold%20mining%20companies%2C%20Kertsos%20models%20their%20performance%20under%20different%20gold%20prices%20to%20ensure%20they're%20resilient%20to%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20underlying%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20to%20stress%20test%20the%20balance%20sheet%20and%20the%20cash%20cost%20curve%20of%20the%20gold%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Kertsos%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20gold%20price%20goes%20lower%20by%20one%2C%20two%2C%20or%20three%20standard%20deviations%2C%20how%20does%20the%20gold%20stock%20behave%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20in%20gold%20mines%20also%20requires%20due%20diligence%20beyond%20just%20looking%20at