0firm%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20had%20standing%20to%20sue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBates%20said%20it%20was%20clear%20Jenner%20%26amp%3B%20Block%20was%20harmed%20because%20the%20whole%20point%20of%20Trump's%20order%20was%20to%20single%20out%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20executive%20order%20talks%20about%20Jenner%20and%20cutting%20off%20money%20to%20Jenner%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20said%2C%20sounding%20incredulous.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20trying%20to%20punish%20Jenner%20by%20stopping%20the%20flow%20of%20money%20to%20Jenner.%20Well%2C%20I%20think%20it%20seems%20to%20me%20to%20be%20on%20its%20face%20sufficient%20for%20standing%20purposes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20if%20the%20court%20is%20so%20inclined%E2%80%94%26quot%3B%20Lawson%20began%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTell%20me%20why%20I%20shouldn't%20be%20so%20inclined%3F%26quot%3B%20Bates%20snapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c307a01-87f9-44ca-96c5-07a10132a96f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20solo%20act%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELawson%20was%20joined%20on%20the%20court%20docket%20by%20Chad%20Mizelle%2C%20Bondi's%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20when%20defending%20the%20government%20against%20the%20first%20Big%20Law%20lawsuit%2C%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaw-firms-fight-trump-attack-big-law-unprecedented-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerkins%20Coie%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Lawson%20has%20been%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20their%20names%20aren't%20on%20the%20court%20docket%2C%20other%20attorneys%20are%20most%20likely%20helping%20Lawson%20write%20his%20briefs%20and%20doing%20legal%20research%20to%20defend%20Trump's%20executive%20orders%2C%20according%20to%20Ellen%20Blain%2C%20who%20previously%20supervised%20the%20civil%20division%20within%20the%20Manhattan%20US%20attorney's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20matter%20of%20resources%20and%20work%2C%20obviously%2C%20o