%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20weren't%20planning%20to%20have%20another%20kid.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20my%20wife%20was%2038%2C%20and%20she%20didn't%20think%20she%20could%20get%20pregnant%20again.%20It%20was%20so%20joyful%20to%20add%20Eddie%20to%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20stepkids%20don't%20share%20my%20last%20name%2C%20I%20love%20all%20three%20of%20my%20kids%20and%20decided%20to%20divide%20my%20assets%20equally%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20assets%2C%20as%20does%20my%20wife%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20a%20nurse%20practitioner%20in%20aesthetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286d23057-e262-4173-8576-7229a21b3fb2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20put%20together%20a%20trust%20at%20age%2040%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20kids%20would%20all%20be%20protected.%20My%20baby%20brother%20died%20of%20an%20overdose.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F12-famous-people-who-died-without-will-picasso-prince-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edidn't%20have%20a%20will%20or%20trust%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20his%20case%20is%20still%20in%20probate.%20The%20courts%20are%20backed%20up%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20mess.%20We%20don't%20want%20our%20kids%20ever%20to%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20placed%20our%20assets%20inside%20a%20living%20trust%20and%20equally%20split%20everything%2C%20including%20a%20%243M%20house%2C%20a%20%241M%20doctor%20practice%2C%20and%20%24800%2C000%20in%20retirement%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20plan%20to%20max%20out%20all%20the%20kids'%20retirement%20accounts%20and%20HSA%20accounts%20annually.%20If%20the%20economy%20grows%2C%20those%20accounts%20should%20continue%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8610579-8bf6-4529-ab5b-77a0b76ee9e7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20older%20kids%20didn't%20care%20much%20at%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20told%20the%20older%20kids%20about%20the%20trust%2C%20they%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20whatever%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20returned%20to%20playing%20video%20games.%20More%20recently%2C%20we%20discussed%20the%20trust%20with%20them%20again%2C%20and%20Mckyle%20appreciated%20that%20it%20was%20split%20equally%20among%20all%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlicia%20said%20poignantly%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20ability%20to%20leave%20behind%20a%20piece%20of%20yourself%20with%20those%20you%20trust%20to%20carry%20your%20name%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef7b45b0-6691-4ff9-8430-04ea228085a1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202024%2C%20I%20had%20a%20health%20scare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20in%20for%20a%20routine%20physical%2C%20and%20my%20doctor%20said%20after%2040%2C%20I%20should%20get%20a%20%26quot%3Bcoronary%20calcium%20score%26quot%3B%20since%20I%20have%20a%20family%20history%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20on%20my%20dad's%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfterward%2C%20further%20tests%20and%20scans%20were%20recommended%2C%20and%20what%20is%20commonly%20called%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-had-widow-maker-heart-attack-while-playing-golf-survived-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidow%20maker%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20was%20found%20to%20be%20a%20blockage%20to%20the%20LAD%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20arteries%20that%20supply%20blood%20to%20the%20heart%20muscle.%20The%20nickname%20is%20due%20to%20its%20lack%20of%20symptoms%20when%20blocked%2C%20sometimes%20resulting%20in%20men%20suddenly%20dying%20from%20massive%20heart%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20the%20results%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20ER%2C%20and%20my%20cardiologist%20recommended%20an%20angiogram.%20He%20removed%20a%2090%25%20blockage.%20It's%20scary%2C%20and%20I%20could've%20died%20if%20we%20didn't%20catch%20it.%20It%20brought%20to%20reality%20that%20life%20is%20very%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-have-retirement-p