s%20others%20with%20similar%20qualifications.%26quot%3B%20Or%20pay%20just%20%2437%20a%20month%20and%20%26quot%3Bgain%20instant%20access%20to%20cutting-edge%20online%20strategies%20that%20are%20working%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%20For%20the%20purposes%20of%20this%20story%2C%20I%20took%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tweets-take-the-red-pill-what-it-means-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ered%20pill%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20Launchpad%20%26quot%3Bequips%20you%20for%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20website%20reads%2C%20by%20teaching%20you%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20making%20money%20through%20online%20ventures%20and%20helping%20you%20make%20your%20first%20%241%2C000%20online.%20(Another%20Gadzhi%20program%2C%20Agency%20Accelerator%2C%20costs%20%241%2C500.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20opening%20Digital%20Launchpad%2C%20I'm%20greeted%20with%20an%20introduction%20video%20by%20Gadzhi%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Unf*ck%20Your%20Life.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life.%20And%20most%20importantly%2C%20welcome%20to%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20He%20speaks%20in%20a%20confident%2C%20flat%20tone%20while%20gazing%20into%20the%20camera%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20approach%20deployed%20by%20the%20dozens%20of%20young%2C%20male%20online-course%20gurus%20I%20received%20ads%20for%20while%20reporting%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatching%20Gadzhi's%20tutorials%20at%20times%20feels%20like%20reading%20a%20paragraph-long%20summary%20of%20a%20book.%20Details%20on%20effective%20business%20strategy%20are%20often%20thin%20and%20rote.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Gadzhi%20makes%20a%20point%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20packaging%20by%20saying%20that%20consumers%20choose%20their%20ice%20cream%20based%20on%20the%20best-looking%20cartons%2C%20before%20moving%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20other%20programs%20in%20its%20orbit%2C%20Digital%20Launchpa