pener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326836%2Fsai-vignesh-rescuer-activist-started-almighty-animal-care-trust-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesperate%20for%20just%20a%20little%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20water%20to%20get%20through%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20People%20for%20Animals%20(PfA)%2C%20in%20March%202024%20alone%2C%20over%2088.2%20per%20cent%20of%20birds%2C%20and%205.9%20percent%20of%20reptiles%20and%20mammals%20rescued%20were%20found%20to%20be%20dehydrated.%20If%20these%20numbers%20are%20alarming%20in%20a%20relatively%20greener%20city%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20with%20its%20harsher%2C%20drier%20climate%20%E2%80%94%20is%20even%20more%20dire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20seven%20friends%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Bawarla%20near%20Jodhpur%20decided%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20stand%20by%20and%20watch.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20simple%20effort%20to%20place%20bowls%20of%20water%20and%20grain%20for%20animals%20has%20transformed%20into%20%E2%80%98Jeev%20Jantu%20Premee%20Bandhu%20Sanstha%E2%80%99%20(Friends%20Who%20Love%20Living%20Beings)%2C%20a%20grassroots%20movement%20with%20over%20690%20active%20members%20across%2035%20villages%2C%20all%20united%20by%20one%20mission%3A%20to%20ensure%20no%20living%20being%20dies%20of%20thirst%20or%20hunger%20during%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20punishing%20summers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeaths%20due%20to%20dehydration%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20regions%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20temperatures%20often%20soar%20above%2045%C2%B0C%2C%20dehydration%20can%20prove%20fatal%20for%20animals.%20This%20became%20painfully%20c